33},{"type":710},{"text":9105,"type":75,"marks":9106}," The software intelligently assigns dock doors based on various factors such as shipment priority, trailer contents, and dock availability. This optimization leads to smoother operations and reduced waiting times.",[9107],{"type":149,"attrs":9108},{"color":1233},{"type":2370,"content":9110},[9111],{"type":112,"attrs":9112,"content":9113},{"textAlign":139},[9114,9120],{"text":9115,"type":75,"marks":9116},"Real-time Visibility:",[9117,9119],{"type":149,"attrs":9118},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"text":9121,"type":75,"marks":9122}," With YMS, you no longer have to rely on outdated spreadsheets or radio communications. Instead, you can access a live digital map that provides information about the location and status of every asset in your yard.",[9123],{"type":149,"attrs":9124},{"color":1233},{"type":2370,"content":9126},[9127],{"type":112,"attrs":9128,"content":9129},{"textAlign":139},[9130,9136],{"text":9131,"type":75,"marks":9132},"Automated Workflows:",[9133,9135],{"type":149,"attrs":9134},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"text":9137,"type":75,"marks":9138}," The system automates repetitive manual tasks by triggering actions based on predefined rules. For example, it can send notifications when trailers arrive or automatically generate move tasks for yard drivers.",[9139],{"type":149,"attrs":9140},{"color":1233},{"type":69,"attrs":9142,"content":9143},{"level":2670,"textAlign":139},[9144],{"text":9145,"type":75,"marks":9146},"Benefits of Using YMS",[9147,9149],{"type":149,"attrs":9148},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"type":2367,"content":9151},[9152,9162,9172],{"type":2370,"content":9153},[9154],{"type":112,"attrs":9155,"content":9156},{"textAlign":139},[9157],{"text":9158,"type":75,"marks":9159},"Improved Efficiency: By streamlining processes and eliminating manual errors, YMS helps businesses operate more efficiently.",[9160],{"type":149,"attrs":9161},{"color":1233},{"type":2370,"content":9163},[9164],{"type":112,"a